HEADWORD: Cowwheat
<hw>Cow"wheat`</hw> <pr>(-hw?t`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A weed of the genus <gen>Melampyrum</gen>, with black seeds, found
on European wheatfields.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

